<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 20:07:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>人质父亲敦促美国保守派犹太人放弃对哈马斯“全面胜利”的“幻想”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/hostages-father-tells-conservative-u-s-jews-there-wont-be-total-victory-over-hamas/0000018f-df5f-d36a-a1ff-ffffcac80000</link><description>乔纳森·德克尔-陈表示，确保人质获释的唯一方法是“与撒旦谈判”，他的言论赢得了礼貌而柔和的掌声</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 19:36:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/hostages-father-tells-conservative-u-s-jews-there-wont-be-total-victory-over-hamas/0000018f-df5f-d36a-a1ff-ffffcac80000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔是一名因公众恐惧而无法直视人质家庭的部长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-03/ty-article/.highlight/ben-gvir-is-a-minister-fueled-by-public-fear-who-cant-look-hostage-families-in-the-eye/0000018f-df00-d36a-a1ff-fff448010000</link><description>“民粹主义”这个词经常出现在极右翼煽动者、国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔的简介中。那么当他说他已经看够了时，他是什么意思呢？</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 19:16:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-03/ty-article/.highlight/ben-gvir-is-a-minister-fueled-by-public-fear-who-cant-look-hostage-families-in-the-eye/0000018f-df00-d36a-a1ff-fff448010000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击中拯救以色列家庭的狗去世</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/dog-who-saved-israeli-family-during-october-7-hamas-attack-dies/0000018f-df1b-d617-afbf-df3b35230000</link><description>佩特尔（Petel）是本-兹维（Ben-Zvi）一家心爱的狗，它用吠叫吓跑了袭击者，并在与家人失散后几天内被枪杀，最终在去世前与家人团聚。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 18:15:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/dog-who-saved-israeli-family-during-october-7-hamas-attack-dies/0000018f-df1b-d617-afbf-df3b35230000</guid></item><item><title>“如果哈马斯同意这一提议，内塔尼亚胡就没有退出路线。他不能说不&amp;#39;</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/if-hamas-agrees-to-the-offer-netanyahu-has-no-exit-route-he-cant-say-no/0000018f-deb5-d244-a38f-dff5df6b0000</link><description>一位熟悉最新事态发展的消息人士的这句话强调了等待内塔尼亚胡的戏剧性一周以及他可能付出的代价。然而，对于以色列选民来说，这并不一定令人担忧</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 18:04:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/if-hamas-agrees-to-the-offer-netanyahu-has-no-exit-route-he-cant-say-no/0000018f-deb5-d244-a38f-dff5df6b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队：四名人质被活捉到加沙被杀，可能是以色列国防军的炮火造成的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/israeli-army-four-hostages-taken-alive-to-gaza-were-killed-possibly-by-idf-fire/0000018f-dede-db27-ab9f-dfff16f70000</link><description>10 月 7 日，所有四名人质均被哈马斯绑架 ■ 以色列军队检查他们是否在汗尤尼斯被以色列国防军炮火打死</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 17:45:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/israeli-army-four-hostages-taken-alive-to-gaza-were-killed-possibly-by-idf-fire/0000018f-dede-db27-ab9f-dfff16f70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 241 天：正统派联盟部长表示他的政党支持人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-241-haredi-coalition-minister-says-his-party-backs-hostage-deal/0000018f-def8-db29-a3ef-fffa0e5e0001</link><description>内塔尼亚胡总理：拜登总统的停火提议不会停止战争，只会导致暂时休战以释放人质 ■ 以色列国防军表示正在对以色列监狱中关押的 48 名加沙人死亡事件进行刑事调查 ■ 巴勒斯坦总统阿巴斯表示“伊朗旨在最高领袖哈梅内伊称哈马斯 10 月 7 日的袭击“来得正是时候”，“牺牲巴勒斯坦人的鲜血” ■ 以下是战争进入 241 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 17:00:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-241-haredi-coalition-minister-says-his-party-backs-hostage-deal/0000018f-def8-db29-a3ef-fffa0e5e0001</guid></item><item><title>解释：承认巴勒斯坦作为一个国家意味着什么？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/explained-what-happens-when-a-country-recognizes-palestine-as-a-state/0000018f-ddba-df43-a7df-fdfae7ad0000</link><description>西班牙、挪威、爱尔兰和斯洛文尼亚上个月都承认了巴勒斯坦国，这意味着现在有 145 个国家正式承认巴勒斯坦人与以色列一起在自己的国家生活的权利。但它在实践中到底意味着什么呢？</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 15:55:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/explained-what-happens-when-a-country-recognizes-palestine-as-a-state/0000018f-ddba-df43-a7df-fdfae7ad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将哈米吉多顿的“耶稣马赛克”借给有争议的圣经博物馆</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-06-03/ty-article/israel-lending-jesus-mosaic-from-armageddon-to-controversial-bible-museum-in-u-s/0000018f-dd63-d513-a9af-ff7387770000</link><description>在从监狱中移走的极早期基督教祈祷厅中发现的马赛克，将在华盛顿特区福音派支持的圣经博物馆展出</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 15:25:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-06-03/ty-article/israel-lending-jesus-mosaic-from-armageddon-to-controversial-bible-museum-in-u-s/0000018f-dd63-d513-a9af-ff7387770000</guid></item><item><title>叙利亚消息人士称，伊朗附属民兵成员在以色列袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/syrian-sources-say-iranian-affiliated-militia-members-killed-in-israeli-strike/0000018f-de70-d9db-ad9f-fffed6df0000</link><description>叙利亚军队发动的袭击袭击了数个大院，造成16名武装分子死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 15:19:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/syrian-sources-say-iranian-affiliated-militia-members-killed-in-israeli-strike/0000018f-de70-d9db-ad9f-fffed6df0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列南部豺狼撕咬婴儿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/jackal-mauls-baby-in-southern-israel/0000018f-de4e-d36f-a3ef-fe7fc5450000</link><description>这名婴儿从露营帐篷中被抢走，受伤但情况稳定，几周后在内盖夫发生的另一起事件中，一名 9 岁的孩子被狼拖走并咬伤</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 14:49:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/jackal-mauls-baby-in-southern-israel/0000018f-de4e-d36f-a3ef-fe7fc5450000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列政府对胜利有着扭曲的看法。加沙战争对他们来说更像是一场十字军东征”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-03/ty-article-podcast/israels-government-has-a-distorted-view-of-victory-for-them-the-war-is-more-a-crusade/0000018f-dd8a-df43-a7df-fdcaa4330000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 14:39:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-03/ty-article-podcast/israels-government-has-a-distorted-view-of-victory-for-them-the-war-is-more-a-crusade/0000018f-dd8a-df43-a7df-fdcaa4330000</guid></item><item><title>亲以色列支持者对马尔代夫旅行禁令表示愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/pro-israel-supporters-express-outrage-on-x-over-maldives-travel-ban/0000018f-de30-d36f-a3ef-fe772d4a0000</link><description>一位 X 用户表示，“多米尼加共和国存在，谁还需要马尔代夫”。针对马尔代夫新禁令，以色列外交部发出警告，敦促以色列人不要前往该国</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 14:35:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/pro-israel-supporters-express-outrage-on-x-over-maldives-travel-ban/0000018f-de30-d36f-a3ef-fe772d4a0000</guid></item><item><title>只要与极端正统派的政治协议占上风，以色列人就会继续陷入交通堵塞</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israelis-will-remain-stuck-in-traffic-due-to-coercion-by-the-ultra-orthodox/0000018f-dd7d-d513-a9af-ff7d8cf40000</link><description>多年来，对极端正统政党的政治依赖一直拖延着以色列最大的交通项目，并使它们变得更加昂贵。里雄莱锡安-莫迪因新线的铁路桥只是最新的例子</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 14:08:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israelis-will-remain-stuck-in-traffic-due-to-coercion-by-the-ultra-orthodox/0000018f-dd7d-d513-a9af-ff7d8cf40000</guid></item><item><title>面对日益严重的危机，内塔尼亚胡打出了他仅剩的一张牌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/faced-with-multiplying-crises-netanyahu-plays-the-only-card-he-has-left/0000018f-ddb6-d622-a1bf-dfb617640000</link><description>解散以色列议会将使内塔尼亚胡摆脱极右翼伙伴的否决，并朝着与哈马斯达成协议的方向迈进，同时避免法院关于征召极端正统派以色列人的爆炸性决定</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 12:39:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/faced-with-multiplying-crises-netanyahu-plays-the-only-card-he-has-left/0000018f-ddb6-d622-a1bf-dfb617640000</guid></item><item><title>作为国际刑事法院第一任首席检察官，以色列领导人仍然可以通过这种方式避免战争罪审判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-iccs-first-chief-prosecutor-heres-how-israeli-leaders-can-avoid-war-crimes-trial/0000018f-c9d7-db12-a3ff-cbf7fe470000</link><description>国际刑事法院检察官只有一种方法可以决定针对以色列总理内塔尼亚胡和国防部长加兰特的案件不可受理。问题是以色列及其司法系统是否愿意采取必要的行动</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 12:32:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-iccs-first-chief-prosecutor-heres-how-israeli-leaders-can-avoid-war-crimes-trial/0000018f-c9d7-db12-a3ff-cbf7fe470000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队对战争期间 48 名加沙人死亡事件进行刑事调查，其中大部分是被拘留者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/idf-conducts-criminal-investigation-into-48-deaths-of-gazans-in-the-war-mostly-detainees/0000018f-dd46-db0d-a98f-dd4f27950000</link><description>以色列国防军宪兵已启动数十起涉及士兵行为的刑事调查，其中包括涉嫌抢劫、盗窃武器、暴力和不服从命令的案件。然而，尚未对涉及加沙死亡的案件提出任何指控</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 10:44:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/idf-conducts-criminal-investigation-into-48-deaths-of-gazans-in-the-war-mostly-detainees/0000018f-dd46-db0d-a98f-dd4f27950000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部揭示了穿过戈兰高地的未知罗马道路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-06-03/ty-article-magazine/unknown-roman-road-revealed-cutting-through-golan-heights/0000018f-dd32-d673-ab8f-fffa5d410000</link><description>为什么罗马人修建了一条从加利利海到叙利亚纳瓦的道路，完全忽略了途中的许多村庄？</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 09:08:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-06-03/ty-article-magazine/unknown-roman-road-revealed-cutting-through-golan-heights/0000018f-dd32-d673-ab8f-fffa5d410000</guid></item><item><title>加沙边境基布兹发现疑似哈马斯自 10 月 7 日以来被谋杀的以色列人尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/body-of-murdered-israeli-presumed-hostage-since-oct-7-found-in-gaza-border-kibbutz/0000018f-dcff-d000-adbf-ddff22700000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布，10 月 7 日被哈马斯杀害的多列夫·雅胡德 (Dolev Yahoud) 的遗体在尼尔奥兹基布兹 (Kibbutz Nir ​​Oz) 被发现。雅胡德的妹妹阿贝尔与她的搭档阿里尔·科尼奥和他的兄弟大卫·科尼奥仍被哈马斯关押</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 08:34:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/body-of-murdered-israeli-presumed-hostage-since-oct-7-found-in-gaza-border-kibbutz/0000018f-dcff-d000-adbf-ddff22700000</guid></item><item><title>拉法过境点可能是巴勒斯坦权力机构返回加沙的催化剂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/the-rafah-crossing-may-be-the-catalyst-for-the-return-of-the-palestinian-authority-to-gaza/0000018f-db8a-dd44-a3ef-db8b55e90000</link><description>正如开罗代表团在最近关于重新开放过境点寻求援助的峰会上所说，拉法是“巴勒斯坦-埃及过境点”。尽管以色列试图抵抗，巴勒斯坦权力机构可能是管理过境点和加沙本身的唯一现实选择</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 02:49:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/the-rafah-crossing-may-be-the-catalyst-for-the-return-of-the-palestinian-authority-to-gaza/0000018f-db8a-dd44-a3ef-db8b55e90000</guid></item><item><title>失去控制：以色列在加沙缺乏进展波及黎巴嫩边境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-distances-himself-from-the-cease-fire-deal-he-already-agreed-too/0000018f-da59-dbdb-a59f-db59468c0000</link><description>真主党在黎巴嫩方面的损失明显更高，因为他们对以色列北部深处进行了猛烈炮击。随着公众对以色列政府采取行动的压力越来越大，全面战争的可能性迫在眉睫，带来更大的破坏</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 02:48:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-distances-himself-from-the-cease-fire-deal-he-already-agreed-too/0000018f-da59-dbdb-a59f-db59468c0000</guid></item></channel></rss>